Healthy snack dips under 5minutes 🏃🏻‍♀️

Recipe 1: guadomole dip
Ingredients: avocado, tomato, onion, chilli flakes, oregano, black pepper, black salt

Recipe 2: salsa
Ingredients: tomato, onion, jalapeño, coriander, lemon juice, black pepper, salt

Recipe 3: protein dip
Ingredients: paneer, curd, milk, parsley, oregano, chilli flakes, salt

Recipe 1:
Oats smoothie

Ingredients:
One scoop oats
One scoop flavoured protein powder
Milk
Banana

Just blend everything together and enjoy 💪🏻

Recipe 2
protein + oats = proats

Microwave one scoop oats with milk for 3minutes.
Mix in your flavoured protein powder, top up with your fav fruits, nuts and seeds and enjoyyy 

Recipe 3

Mix together one scoop unflavoured protein powder and milk. Add granola with your fav fruits and enjoyy 🥤

All of them have more than 40gm of protein and will keep you full for hours!
